name: TT1-C - ApeChad to the Moon - LiftOff Edition
description: In the never-ending search for the greatest gainz ApeChad has suited up for a mission to Mars filled with hope and trepidation for his long journey. Liftoff brought a tense moment as ApeChad almost lost his grip upon his fiery TezTools powered steed but now as ApeChad reaches the higher atmosphere hodling on is easier while the craft begins making impressively fast gainz right from the start. Many trials and tribulations are sure to come on a journey across the stars, will ApeChad reach Mars or will some unknown fate befall ApeChad on the way?
